sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as REST API Controller
    participant Auth as Auth Middleware
    participant Service as Job Application Service
    participant DB as MongoDB

    User ->> FE: Enter job details and submit form
    FE ->> FE: Validate input data
    FE ->> API: POST /jobs (JWT + job data)

    API ->> Auth: Verify JWT token
    Auth -->> API: Token valid

    API ->> Service: createJobApplication(data, userId)
    Service ->> DB: Insert JobApplication
    DB -->> Service: JobID created

    Service -->> API: Success response
    API -->> FE: 201 Created + JobID
    FE -->> User: Confirmation shown
